node.text: Gave @xgames high air my best shot yesterday and ended up 🥈 I learned a lot the whole day and now know what I need to work on to come back swinging next time ⚔️ HUGE props to everyone that came out to the #SLAYGROUND and sent it. It was crazy to see my place put to its full potential and was an honor to host the event. THANK YOU everyone that made this possible 🙏🏼
